column2: select p.objid, p.specObjID, p.ra, p.dec, p.g, p.r, g.h_alpha_flux, g.nii_flux from GalSpecLine as g join photoObj as p ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid join dbo.fgetnearbyobjeq (#, #, #) n on p.objid = n.objid join specObj s on p.objid = s.bestobjid where p.petrorad_r > # and p.r < # and s.Class = # and s.z > = #
